<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4669316>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. (A–D) Pilargis angeli n. sp. UANL-1474: (A) anterior end in dorsal view (verrucae are mostly restricted to parapodia); (B) right setiger 10 in anterior view; (C) median setiger in anterior view; (D) right setiger 60 in anterior view. (E) Pilargis sp. juvenile BLM 85401 BF1, complete organism in dorsal view, slightly distorted by cover slip. Scale bars: 225 mm (A); 120 mm (B–D); 500 mm (E)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4669316/files/figure.png" .

